1. Warning / Alert / Status / Problem

(Emojis indicating something requires attention, is wrong, dangerous, important, or represents a status)
⚠️ (Warning)
⛔ (No Entry / Forbidden)
🚫 (Prohibited)
🚨 (Police Light / Emergency Alert)
🔴 (Red Circle - Often used for Record/Stop/Critical Alert)
❗ (Exclamation Mark - Alert / Importance)
❌ (Cross Mark - Error / Incorrect / Stop)
🛑 (Stop Sign - Halt / Critical Warning)
🚩 (Flag - Flagged Issue / Marker)
📌 (Pushpin - Important Notice / Pinned Item)
❓ (Question Mark - Uncertainty / Query / Problem)
